---
title: Grilled Chicken & Steak Fajitas with Charred Veggies, Cilantro Pineapple Pico & Smoky Red Pepper Crema
description: When it comes to fajitas, we like to think that filling your tortilla is an art form. And, since every culinary masterpiece should have multiple textures, flavors, and colors, this one has it all: charred veggies, sweet and spicy cilantro pineapple pico, and creamy smoky red pepper crema. Plus, no need to stare at the menu and debate the age-old question: steak or chicken? These fajitas have both!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/grilled-chicken-steak-fajitas-00e4f0bc.jpg
